Document: PinJoint2D  
Path: godot/classes/class_pinjoint2d.rst  
Summary: A 2D physics joint that connects two bodies at a single point, enabling rotation while maintaining a fixed connection.  

A physics joint that attaches two 2D physics bodies at a single point, allowing them to freely rotate. Note: Can be used to attach a RigidBody2D to a StaticBody2D, creating a pendulum or seesaw effect.
