Document: PinJoint2D
Path: godot/classes/class_pinjoint2d.rst
Summary: Properties for configuring angular limits, motor behavior, and joint softness in a 2D pin joint.

- angular_limit_enabled (bool): Enables angular limits. Default: false.
- angular_limit_lower (float): Lower bound for angular limit. Default: 0.0.
- angular_limit_upper (float): Upper bound for angular limit. Default: 0.0.
- motor_enabled (bool): Enables motor-driven angular velocity. Default: false.
- motor_target_velocity (float): Target angular velocity for motor. Default: 0.0.
- softness (float): Determines joint compliance (lower = stiffer). Default: 0.0.
